<paragraph id="8BD036D36428FF80FF1AF74D4878C73F" blockId="24.[187,1398,265,362]" pageId="24" pageNumber="25">16, 19BAI 23, 19BAI 27-2, 19BAI 37, 19BAI 39, 19BAI 43, 19BAI 44, 19BAI 55, 19BAI 58, Tangbagou Formation, Blue Snake section, latest Famennian–Tournaisian, late Devonian–early Carboniferous (this work).</paragraph>
